    "description": "<p>At <strong>Speech Academy Asia</strong>, we believe that every child can be transformed into confident speakers, regardless who they are, or what their future career path is, by equipping each and every one of our young aspiring leaders with the right tools to speak up without fears.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This therefore, summarizes our overarching philosophy of “The Key to Communications” – An array of social interaction and public speaking skillsets that allows us to speak up and have a voice of our own, both verbally and non-verbally, while living up to our fullest potential.</p>",
